He already told the radio "Český rozhlas" that he chose specifically to sing the variants alone, the singers with the most representative young voices, which are expressive and popular.
"From the beginning I tried to take care that both and even the choir, have the clear statement, that the text is well understandable, that it is in harmony," he said.
Then the national anthem will celebrate next year's 175th anniversary.
